{
  "chapter": {
    "id": "kjva:first-chronicles.3",
    "translationId": "kjva",
    "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
    "chapterNumber": 3,
    "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3",
    "summary": "Source text for 1 Chronicles 3 in King James Version with Apocrypha."
  },
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": "kjva:first-chronicles.3.1",
      "translationId": "kjva",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:1",
      "text": "Now these were the sons of David, which were born unto him in Hebron; the firstborn Amnon, of Ahinoam the Jezreelitess; the second Daniel, of Abigail the Carmelitess:",
      "paragraphStart": true
    },
    {
      "id": "kjva:first-chronicles.3.2",
      "translationId": "kjva",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:2",
      "text": "The third, Absalom the son of Maachah the daughter of Talmai king of Geshur: the fourth, Adonijah the son of Haggith:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "kjva:first-chronicles.3.3",
      "translationId": "kjva",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:3",
      "text": "The fifth, Shephatiah of Abital: the sixth, Ithream by Eglah his wife.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "kjva:first-chronicles.3.4",
      "translationId": "kjva",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:4",
      "text": "These six were born unto him in Hebron; and there he reigned seven years and six months: and in Jerusalem he reigned thirty and three years.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "kjva:first-chronicles.3.5",
      "translationId": "kjva",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:5",
      "text": "And these were born unto him in Jerusalem; Shimea, and Shobab, and Nathan, and Solomon, four, of Bath–shua the daughter of Ammiel:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "kjva:first-chronicles.3.6",
      "translationId": "kjva",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:6",
      "text": "Ibhar also, and Elishama, and Eliphelet,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "kjva:first-chronicles.3.7",
      "translationId": "kjva",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:7",
      "text": "And Nogah, and Nepheg, and Japhia,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "kjva:first-chronicles.3.8",
      "translationId": "kjva",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:8",
      "text": "And Elishama, and Eliada, and Eliphelet, nine.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "kjva:first-chronicles.3.9",
      "translationId": "kjva",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:9",
      "text": "These were all the sons of David, beside the sons of the concubines, and Tamar their sister.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "kjva:first-chronicles.3.10",
      "translationId": "kjva",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:10",
      "text": "And Solomon’s son was Rehoboam, Abia his son, Asa his son, Jehoshaphat his son,",
      "paragraphStart": true
    },
    {
      "id": "kjva:first-chronicles.3.11",
      "translationId": "kjva",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 11,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:11",
      "text": "Joram his son, Ahaziah his son, Joash his son,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "kjva:first-chronicles.3.12",
      "translationId": "kjva",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 12,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:12",
      "text": "Amaziah his son, Azariah his son, Jotham his son,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "kjva:first-chronicles.3.13",
      "translationId": "kjva",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 13,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:13",
      "text": "Ahaz his son, Hezekiah his son, Manasseh his son,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "kjva:first-chronicles.3.14",
      "translationId": "kjva",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 14,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:14",
      "text": "Amon his son, Josiah his son.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "kjva:first-chronicles.3.15",
      "translationId": "kjva",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 15,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:15",
      "text": "And the sons of Josiah were, the firstborn Johanan, the second Jehoiakim, the third Zedekiah, the fourth Shallum.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "kjva:first-chronicles.3.16",
      "translationId": "kjva",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 16,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:16",
      "text": "And the sons of Jehoiakim: Jeconiah his son, Zedekiah his son.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "kjva:first-chronicles.3.17",
      "translationId": "kjva",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 17,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:17",
      "text": "And the sons of Jeconiah; Assir, Salathiel his son,",
      "paragraphStart": true
    },
    {
      "id": "kjva:first-chronicles.3.18",
      "translationId": "kjva",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 18,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:18",
      "text": "Malchiram also, and Pedaiah, and Shenazar, Jecamiah, Hoshama, and Nedabiah.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "kjva:first-chronicles.3.19",
      "translationId": "kjva",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 19,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:19",
      "text": "And the sons of Pedaiah were, Zerubbabel, and Shimei: and the sons of Zerubbabel; Meshullam, and Hananiah, and Shelomith their sister:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "kjva:first-chronicles.3.20",
      "translationId": "kjva",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 20,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:20",
      "text": "And Hashubah, and Ohel, and Berechiah, and Hasadiah, Jushab–hesed, five.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "kjva:first-chronicles.3.21",
      "translationId": "kjva",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 21,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:21",
      "text": "And the sons of Hananiah; Pelatiah, and Jesaiah: the sons of Rephaiah, the sons of Arnan, the sons of Obadiah, the sons of Shechaniah.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "kjva:first-chronicles.3.22",
      "translationId": "kjva",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 22,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:22",
      "text": "And the sons of Shechaniah; Shemaiah: and the sons of Shemaiah; Hattush, and Igeal, and Bariah, and Neariah, and Shaphat, six.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "kjva:first-chronicles.3.23",
      "translationId": "kjva",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 23,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:23",
      "text": "And the sons of Neariah; Elioenai, and Hezekiah, and Azrikam, three.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "kjva:first-chronicles.3.24",
      "translationId": "kjva",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 24,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:24",
      "text": "And the sons of Elioenai were, Hodaiah, and Eliashib, and Pelaiah, and Akkub, and Johanan, and Dalaiah, and Anani, seven.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    }
  ]
}
